videos.description: J.P. Macura knocks down an early 3-pointer from the corner for the Musketeers forcing Baylor to call a timeout.
videos.headline: Macura hits corner 3 for Xavier

videos.description: J.P. Macura is off to a hot start for Xavier as he hits a deep 3 to give the Musketeers a 12-point lead.
videos.headline: Macura knocks down big 3 for Xavier

videos.description: Naji Marshall is quick with his hands for the offensive rebound and putback dunk for Xavier.
videos.headline: Marshall gets rebound and jam for Musketeers

videos.description: Manu Lecomte gets open and cuts Xavier's lead to 29-30 with a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Lecomte cuts lead with 3 for Baylor

videos.description: J.P. Macura ends the half with a deep 3-pointer off the glass to put Xavier up five.
videos.headline: Macura banks in 3 at the buzzer

videos.description: Kaiser Gates hits his 4th 3-pointer of the game at the start of the second half for Xavier.
videos.headline: Gates opens 2nd half with quick 3

videos.description: Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. backs down his defender in the paint and turns to make a tough shot for the Bears.
videos.headline: Lual-Acuil hits tough jumper for Baylor

videos.description: Tyrique Jones blocks Manu Lecomte as the shot clock winds down to force the turnover for Xavier.
videos.headline: Jones gets a block on Lecomte

videos.description: Quentin Goodin gets ahead after the steal from J.P. Macura to put Xavier up 55-43 in the second half.
videos.headline: Goodin lays in on the fast-break steal for Xavier

videos.description: Mark Vital speeds down the court and finds space to rock the rim for the Bears.
videos.headline: Vital breaks free on big dunk for Baylor

videos.description: Baylor's Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. gets the steal that transitions into a fast-break layup for Mark Vital.
videos.headline: Baylor steal-and-score cuts into Xavier's lead

videos.description: Kaiser Gates hits his 5th 3-pointer to put Xavier up 72-61 against Baylor late.
videos.headline: Gates knocks down crucial 3 for Xavier
